properties.details: Stunning two bedroom balcony apartment facing the waterfront available 4th February 2024. Situated on the 2nd Floor, the apartment offers a large open plan living room and kitchen space with integrated appliances, dishwasher, fridge/freezer, oven and hob and a separate utility room housing a washer/dryer. Large double bedrooms with walk through wardrobe to en-suite bathrooms with large walk in showers.
